## Upstream dependencies (separate repositories, separate licenses)

This repository does NOT redistribute the Decision Trace Reconstructor (DTR)
itself or the Operational Evidence Plane (OEP) reference implementation; both
are referenced by Zenodo content-addressed DOI in `manifest.yaml`.

- **Decision Trace Reconstructor v0.1.0** —
  Apache-2.0, Zenodo DOI `10.5281/zenodo.19851574`,
  GitHub `governance-evidence/decision-trace-reconstructor`.
- **Operational Evidence Plane v0.1.0** —
  Apache-2.0, Zenodo DOI `10.5281/zenodo.20051037`,
  GitHub `agent-runtime-evidence/operational-evidence-plane`.

